<p>Hi, I'm Mal/Maal! After some coercion it seems as though I've finally come around to putting my art up in some official capacity. I've been drawing SCP-related art for the last few years now, so I've chosen just a few to share with the site that inspired me so much for so long. My art has been featured on here before; recently a <a href="http://securecontainplsno.tumblr.com/">blog I co-run</a> was mentioned on the <a href="/news-11-2016">monthly news</a> (I'm Mod Pink), but all that stuff is silly, and I don't spend too much time on it.</p>
<p>Each image links to the respective article, where possible.</p>
